QuestData.Title: Battle for Azeroth: Tides of War
QuestData.Description:
Champion, the Horde is now at open war with the Alliance.
Our success in this conflict may depend on your skills.
I require your immediate presence in Orgrimmar for a mission of the utmost urgency. Do not keep me waiting.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Nathanos Blightcaller in Orgrimmar.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Nathanos Blightcaller in Orgrimmar.
